T02TD2123E:170a-1: shr'i ae ka rdza t'i bha ga w'a na s'a dha nam /
T02TD2123E:170a-3: dpal bcom ldan 'das ral ba gcig pa'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD2123E:170a-4: rje btsun ral pa pa gcig pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2123E:170a-5: dang por re zhig sngags pas tshogs bsags pa sngon du 'gro bas padma dang /
T02TD2123E:170b-0: ro'i gdan bltas la de'i steng du h'um dang bam las yab dang yum ral pa @170b gcig 'phyang pa'i bcom ldan 'das bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD2123E:170b-3: byang gi padma'i 'dab ma dag la ni rdo rje 'khor lo dang /
T02TD2123E:170b-6: rdo rje sna tshogs rnams bsam mo //
T02TD2123E:170b-7: byang shar la sogs pa'i mtshams bzhir ni bdud rtsi ka p'a la dag go //
T02TD2123E:170b-8: de'i phyi rol du khyams kyi phyogs bzhir gti mug rdo rje ma dkar mo sgron ma thogs pa dang /
T02TD2123E:170b-9: bag chags rdo rje ma ser mo rdo rje thogs pa dang /
T02TD2123E:170b-10: 'dod chags rdo rje ma dmar mo zhags pa thogs pa dang /
T02TD2123E:170b-11: zhe sdang rdo rje ma ljang gu ral gri thogs pa rnams bsgom mo //
T02TD2123E:170b-12: khyams gyi grva bzhir ni byang shar nas brtsams te brtan pa'i rdo rje ma ser mo ri rab thogs pa dang /
T02TD2123E:170b-13: sbyor ba'i rdo rje ma dkar mo zla ba thogs pa dang /
T02TD2123E:170b-14: 'bar ba'i rdo rje ma dmar mo nyi ma thogs pa dang /
T02TD2123E:170b-15: stobs kyi rdo rje ma ljang gu ba dang thogs pa rnams dgod do //
T02TD2123E:170b-16: brgyad po 'di dag ni padma dang ro'i gdan la rnam par dgod pa yin no //
T02TD2123E:170b-19: byang gi sgo bzhir yang go rims ltar rdo rje lcags kyu dang /
T02TD2123E:170b-22: dril bu 'dzin pa rnams dkar ba dang /
T02TD2123E:170b-25: ljang gu'i mdog can rnams bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD2123E:170b-26: ji ltar dam tshig bskyed pa dang /
T02TD2123E:170b-27: ye shes sems dpa' gzhug pa nyid /
T02TD2123E:170b-28: gsang sngags bzlas shing bsgom pa dang //
T02TD2123E:170b-29: rdzogs pa'i rim sogs cho ga bzhin //
T02TD2123E:170b-30: dpal bcom ldan 'das ral pa gcig pa'i man ngag khungs phyung ba /
T02TD2123E:170b-31: slob dpon chen po mi pham sbas pas bsdus pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2123E:170b-33: // / rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug shr'i mi tra dang /
T02TD2123E:170b-34: gnubs lo ts'a ba mee tri shr'is bsgyur ba'o//
